Frequently asked questions



How can I apply for funding for a small environment project?

To find out more about funding for environment projects, please get in touch with your local Unilever careline. You can find their details in the map above. If you cannot find a careline for your country please contact the central careline via the Unilever contact form above.



Where can I get more information about Unilever products in my own country?

Please visit our brands section to find a list of Unilever products that are viewable by country.



I suffer from various allergies. How do I know if your products are suitable for me?

The formulation of our brands varies from country to country, so you need to contact the local careline in the country you live in. Please contact the dedicated careline in your country - you can find details from the map above. If you cannot find your country in the list please use the main Unilever contact form above and we will forward your message on to the relevant team.



