Health
 How is Unilever N.V's financial health and their level of debt?

A company's financial position is much like your own financial position, it includes everything you own (assets) and owe (liabilities).

The boxes below represent the relative size of what makes up Unilever N.V's finances.

The net worth of a company is the difference between its assets and liabilities.



Net Worth 





Unilever N.V short term (1 year) commitments are greater than its holdings of cash and other short term assets.

Unilever N.V's long term commitments exceed its cash and other short term assets.


